# Alex Chen — Operating Context

## Who I Am

I'm Alex Chen, a full-time crypto trader and DeFi researcher. I run:

- **Alpha Trading** — My main trading operation across CEXs and DEXs
- **DeFi Research** — Deep research into protocols, yield strategies, and emerging chains

I operate multiple positions, research threads, and partner relationships simultaneously. I need you to be a high-leverage research assistant and analyst — assume I'm always context-switching and brief me fast.

---

## System Architecture

Everything lives in one of four layers:

| Layer | Purpose | Location |
|-------|---------|----------|
| Cloud Storage | Documents, decks, financials, shared files | `~/Work/` |
| Obsidian | Knowledge, notes, CRM, project tracking | `~/Brain/` |
| macOS Finder | Navigation, pinned shortcuts, color tags | Sidebar pinned |
| Claude Code | AI context, templates, automation | This file + entity CLAUDE.md files |

